  "industry_note": "UNS R56401 / ASTM F136 Grade 23 (ELI = Extra Low Interstitial) — medical implant grade Ti-6Al-4V (O ≤ 0.13, N ≤ 0.05, Fe ≤ 0.25, H ≤ 0.012 — Grade 5 의 절반). Lower interstitial = improved ductility + fracture toughness for cyclic loading. Tmax 350°C continuous. 의료 임플란트 (hip stem, knee femoral, dental, spinal cage, fracture plate) — ASTM F136 표준. AM LPBF for patient-specific 임플란트 (FDA cleared).",
